data.description: ***Offering up to $2,000 lender incentive with preferred lender. See private remarks and documents. Seller will also provide a home warranty up to $610 at closing with an acceptable offer.*** Discover refined living in the heart of The Villages of Fireside, where elegance meets comfort. Nestled in a gated community in a serene cul-de-sac with an expansive lot, this lovely brick residence welcomes you with a 2-car garage and charming covered front porch. Step inside to a tile entryway leading to the timeless beauty of vinyl/hardwood flooring throughout. The living room welcomes you with a large arched window, infusing the space with natural light immediately upon entering the home. Enjoy the convenience of an additional family room, adorned with a fireplace, seamlessly extending to a back patio through tasteful French doors, creating a perfect blend of warmth and connection. The kitchen highlights an inviting eat-in space at the bar, fostering an open concept that flows into the family room with additional room for a breakfast nook and an adjacent formal dining room. The spacious Primary bedroom is a haven of tranquility, featuring vaulted ceilings and a private door to the back patio. The ensuite Primary bathroom is a luxurious retreat, offering two separate vanities, a linen closet, his and hers closets, a toilet room, and a spa-like jacuzzi tub with a tiled walk-in shower. Additional bedrooms, thoughtfully placed on the opposite side of the master, share a full bathroom, complemented by a convenient half bath of the kitchen area. Step outside to the covered back patio, where the sprawling lot and mature landscape create a picturesque backdrop, perfect for relaxing evenings. This home transcends the ordinary, offering a lifestyle of sophistication and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make 1991 Embers Court your sanctuary in Middleburg!
